<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.183377>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Paulodora schockaerti n. sp. A, Atrial organs (from a live specimen). B, Prostate stylet type I (from the holotype). P. subcontorta Schockaert, 1982 C, Prostate stylet type I (from a specimen from Zanzibar). P. watsoni n. sp. D, Prostate stylet type I (from the holotype). P. a n c o r a n. sp. E, picture of the prostate stylet type I (from the holotype). P. contortoides n. sp. F, idem (from the holotype), P. contortoides n. sp. F, idem (from the holotype), P. drepanophora n. sp. G, idem (from the holotype), P. porcellus n. sp. H, idem (from the holotype), P. hamifer n. sp. I, idem (from the holotype), P. schockaerti n. sp. J, idem (from the holotype), P. subcontorta Schockaert, 1982 K, idem (from the same specimen as C), P. w a t s o n i n. sp. L, idem (from the holotype)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/183377/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.183376>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Paulodora ancora n. sp. A, Prostate stylet type I (from the holotype). P. contortoides n. sp. B, Caudal body end (from a live specimen). C, Reconstruction of the atrial organs from the left side. D, Prostate stylet type I (from the holotype). E, Prostate stylet type I (from a specimen from La Réuniuon). P. drepanophora n. sp. F, Prostate stylet type I (from the holotype). P. h a m i f e r n. sp. G, Prostate stylet type I (from the holotype). P. porcellus n. sp. H, Prostate stylet type I (from the holotype)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/183376/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

